Class LaundryItem

java.lang.Object
cyprusDryCleanEntities.LaundryItem
public class LaundryItem extends Object
This LaundryItem class represents a laundry item brought in by a customer for cleaning. Each item includes details which are type, quantity, price, notes, and the employee assigned to clean it.
Version:
23.0
Author:
Ferhat Kasim Koc
